      • main

        public static void main(java.lang.String[] args)
        This is the main entry of the package DataCollector. It launches the Data Collector. This involves:
        1. Getting all the collectors in the system using reflection.
        2. Starting the primary and secondary database managers and passing the obtained collector attributes to them
        3. Starting the GUI
        Parameters:
        args - The arguments are ignored
